      "date": "2023-08-02 16:21:25.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nA lot of checks in various LNDs are `rc != 0`, so they'll fail on and return a positive error code. I can see some examples in kgnilnd_startup. Also, some functions return PTR_ERR - which could be positive.",
